<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>世界新闻头条、最新国际新闻、世界突发新闻 - 印度时报</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world</link><description>世界新闻：TOI 带来最新的世界新闻头条、《时事国际》全球突发新闻。深入分析和全球头条新闻。</description><lastBuildDate>Sat, 14 Oct 2023 06:08:02 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>阿富汗北部什叶派清真寺发生爆炸 17人死亡</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/blast-rips-through-shiite-mosque-in-northern-afghanistan-many-casualties-feared/articleshow/104402762.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104402762.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;据医院官员和目击者称，周五祈祷期间，阿富汗北部一座什叶派清真寺发生爆炸，造成至少 17 人死亡，另有 15 人重伤。然而塔利班官员声称，爆炸中只有七人死亡。目前还没有任何恐怖组织立即声称对此次袭击负责。</description><pubDate>Fri, 13 Oct 2023 12:36:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/blast-rips-through-shiite-mosque-in-northern-afghanistan-many-casualties-feared/articleshow/104402762.cms</guid></item><item><title>世卫组织呼吁立即撤销加沙撤离令</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/who-pleads-for-immediate-reversal-of-gaza-evacuation-order-to-protect-health-reduce-suffering/articleshow/104412410.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104412410.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;世界卫生组织（WHO）呼吁在加沙紧急建立人道主义走廊，以确保安全运送援助物资。持续的空袭和关闭边界使平民无处可去。以色列军方已指示加沙北部 110 万人撤离，世界卫生组织称这对患者、卫生工作者和平民来说是灾难性的。</description><pubDate>Sat, 14 Oct 2023 02:45:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/who-pleads-for-immediate-reversal-of-gaza-evacuation-order-to-protect-health-reduce-suffering/articleshow/104412410.cms</guid></item><item><title>以色列称军队在加沙进行小规模袭击以挫败哈马斯组织</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israel-says-troops-carried-out-small-raids-in-gaza-to-thwart-hamas-cells/articleshow/104411859.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104411859.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;以色列宣布在加沙地带与哈马斯的冲突中已从空战转向地面行动。以色列军队在坦克的支援下，对巴勒斯坦火箭人员进行了小规模袭击，并收集了人质位置的信息。内塔尼亚胡总理誓言要摧毁哈马斯，而一些国家则敦促以色列暂缓进攻。</description><pubDate>Sat, 14 Oct 2023 02:15:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israel-says-troops-carried-out-small-raids-in-gaza-to-thwart-hamas-cells/articleshow/104411859.cms</guid></item><item><title>消息人士称，沙特阿拉伯在战争中搁置与以色列的协议，并与伊朗接触</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/saudi-arabia-puts-israel-deal-on-ice-amid-war-engages-with-iran-sources-say/articleshow/104411723.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104411723.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;据报道，随着以色列和哈马斯之间的冲突升级，沙特阿拉伯暂停了与以色列关系正常化的计划。沙特王国还与伊朗进行了接触，沙特王储穆罕默德·本·萨勒曼接到了伊朗总统易卜拉欣·莱西的电话。与以色列关系正常化谈判的推迟表明，以色列对巴勒斯坦人的让步问题将成为未来更重要的优先事项</description><pubDate>Sat, 14 Oct 2023 01:51:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/saudi-arabia-puts-israel-deal-on-ice-amid-war-engages-with-iran-sources-say/articleshow/104411723.cms</guid></item><item><title>“死亡比离开更好”：尽管以色列声称哈马斯将加沙平民用作人盾，但加沙平民拒绝撤离“地狱”</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/death-is-better-than-leaving-gaza-civilians-refuse-to-evacuate-hellhole-despite-israel-claiming-hamas-are-using-them-as-human-shields/articleshow/104411547.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104411547.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;尽管接到了 24 小时撤离通知，但加沙的许多人还是选择留下来面对潜在的死亡，而不是放弃家园。联合国宣布加沙局势难以为继，电力供应被切断，重要资源变得稀缺。哈马斯鼓励人们留在原地，而以色列则认为他们必须消灭这个恐怖组织。联合国对平民流离失所表示关切。</description><pubDate>Sat, 14 Oct 2023 01:54:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/death-is-better-than-leaving-gaza-civilians-refuse-to-evacuate-hellhole-despite-israel-claiming-hamas-are-using-them-as-human-shields/articleshow/104411547.cms</guid></item><item><title>以色列准备入侵加沙，美国看不到下一步计划</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/hamas-israel-war-as-israel-readies-gaza-invasion-us-sees-no-plan-for-whats-next/articleshow/104411430.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104411430.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;拜登政府担心以色列没有针对加沙地带潜在地面入侵的后果的计划。白宫正在敦促以色列超越消灭哈马斯的眼前目标，并考虑长期冲突的后果。美国还担心加沙的人道主义伤亡以及该地区人质和美国公民的命运。</description><pubDate>Sat, 14 Oct 2023 01:34:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/hamas-israel-war-as-israel-readies-gaza-invasion-us-sees-no-plan-for-whats-next/articleshow/104411430.cms</guid></item><item><title>伊朗敦促美国“控制”以色列以避免地区战争</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/iran-urges-us-to-control-israel-to-avert-regional-war/world/middle-east/iran-urges-us-to-control-israel-to-avert-regional-war/articleshow/104411472.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104411571.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;伊朗最高外交官周五在贝鲁特表示，美国必须控制以色列，以避免与哈马斯的战争在地区蔓延，并补充说德黑兰正在寻求维护黎巴嫩的安全。外交部长侯赛因·阿米尔-阿卜杜拉希安表示：“如果美国人想要阻止该地区的战争发展，他们就必须控制以色列。”他补充道，“我们此行的目标之一就是强调黎巴嫩的安全”</description><pubDate>Sat, 14 Oct 2023 01:23:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/iran-urges-us-to-control-israel-to-avert-regional-war/world/middle-east/iran-urges-us-to-control-israel-to-avert-regional-war/articleshow/104411472.cms</guid></item><item><title>真主党表示“准备好”在时机成熟时对以色列采取行动</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/hezbollah-says-prepared-for-action-against-israel-when-time-comes/articleshow/104411418.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104411418.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;伊朗支持的黎巴嫩真主党运动周五表示，将“做好充分准备”，在时机成熟时加入其盟友哈马斯对以色列的战争。他说：“我们已经做好充分准备，当需要采取行动时，我们会采取行动。”</description><pubDate>Sat, 14 Oct 2023 01:14:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/hezbollah-says-prepared-for-action-against-israel-when-time-comes/articleshow/104411418.cms</guid></item><item><title>法国一学校发生刺伤事件 一名教师死亡 两人受伤 疑似恐怖袭击</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/a-teacher-dies-and-2-people-are-wounded-in-a-stabbing-in-a-french-school-terrorism-is-suspected/articleshow/104411047.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104411047.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;法国反恐检察官宣布，他们正在接手对法国北部一所学校周五发生的持刀袭击事件的调查，该袭击事件导致一名教师死亡，另外两人受伤。国家反恐检察厅启动调查，指出此次袭击涉嫌恐怖动机</description><pubDate>Fri, 13 Oct 2023 23:54:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/a-teacher-dies-and-2-people-are-wounded-in-a-stabbing-in-a-french-school-terrorism-is-suspected/articleshow/104411047.cms</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯称，以色列对加沙逃亡车队的袭击造成 70 人死亡，其中大部分是妇女和儿童</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/hamas-says-70-people-mostly-women-and-children-killed-in-israeli-strikes-on-gazas-fleeing-convoys/articleshow/104411652.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104411652.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;哈马斯官员报告称，以色列对离开加沙城的车队进行空袭，导致约 70 人死亡，其中主要是妇女和儿童。空袭针对的是从加沙城向南行驶的三个不同地点的车辆。</description><pubDate>Sat, 14 Oct 2023 01:44:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/hamas-says-70-people-mostly-women-and-children-killed-in-israeli-strikes-on-gazas-fleeing-convoys/articleshow/104411652.cms</guid></item><item><title>埃及反对派候选人结束总统选举竞选活动</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/egyptian-opposition-candidate-ends-campaign-for-presidential-poll/articleshow/104410967.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104410967.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;在即将举行的选举中埃及总统阿卜杜勒·法塔赫·塞西的潜在挑战者艾哈迈德·坦塔维宣布，由于未获得所需数量的公众支持，他将不会参加竞选。坦塔维的竞选团队声称，官员和亲政府暴徒阻碍了他们争取支持的努力，而安全部队则逮捕了他的支持者并阻止了竞选活动。</description><pubDate>Fri, 13 Oct 2023 23:36:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/egyptian-opposition-candidate-ends-campaign-for-presidential-poll/articleshow/104410967.cms</guid></item><item><title>俄罗斯当局在突袭后拘留了被监禁的反对派领导人阿列克谢·纳瓦尔尼的三名律师</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/russian-authorities-detain-3-lawyers-for-imprisoned-opposition-leader-alexei-navalny-after-raids/articleshow/104410950.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104410950.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;俄罗斯反对派领导人阿列克谢·纳瓦尔尼的三名律师在其住宅被搜查后被俄罗斯当局拘留。此举被视为试图进一步孤立纳瓦尔尼。这些律师因被指控参与极端主义团体而成为刑事案件的一部分。纳瓦尔尼自 2021 年 1 月以来一直被监禁，并面临多项指控，他声称这些指控是出于政治动机。</description><pubDate>Fri, 13 Oct 2023 23:30:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/russian-authorities-detain-3-lawyers-for-imprisoned-opposition-leader-alexei-navalny-after-raids/articleshow/104410950.cms</guid></item><item><title>巴勒斯坦人在联合国呼吁以色列停止进攻，世界大国正在考虑选择</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/at-un-palestinians-call-for-halt-to-israeli-offensive-world-powers-mull-options/articleshow/104410847.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104410847.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;巴勒斯坦联合国特使呼吁联合国秘书长安东尼奥·古特雷斯采取更多行动，制止他所说的以色列的“反人类罪”。以色列警告加沙地带近一半人口在计划发动袭击时搬迁。特使表示，目前采取的行动还不够，并敦促采取更多行动来制止暴力。</description><pubDate>Fri, 13 Oct 2023 23:04:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/at-un-palestinians-call-for-halt-to-israeli-offensive-world-powers-mull-options/articleshow/104410847.cms</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯袭击前几天，美国情报部门警告巴以冲突风险增加</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/days-before-hamas-attack-us-intelligence-warned-of-increased-risk-for-palestinian-israeli-conflict/articleshow/104411021.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104411021.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;美国根据以色列分享的信息进行的情报评估警告拜登政府，在最近的哈马斯袭击之前，巴勒斯坦人和以色列人之间发生冲突的风险日益增加。评估表明，哈马斯正准备升级跨境火箭袭击。然而，这些评估并未提供有关攻击规模的具体细节。</description><pubDate>Fri, 13 Oct 2023 23:46:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/days-before-hamas-attack-us-intelligence-warned-of-increased-risk-for-palestinian-israeli-conflict/articleshow/104411021.cms</guid></item><item><title>特朗普表示，在共和党批评内塔尼亚胡“让我们失望”后，他与内塔尼亚胡站在一起</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/trump-says-he-stands-with-netanyahu-after-a-barrage-of-gop-criticism-for-saying-he-let-us-down/articleshow/104410799.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104410799.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;前总统唐纳德·特朗普在社交媒体上使用#IStandWithIsrael 和#IStandWithBibi 标签表达了对以色列和总理本杰明·内塔尼亚胡的支持。此前，特朗普曾批评内塔尼亚胡以及对该国情报机构的评论。尽管特朗普的共和党竞争对手谴责他的言论，但特朗普的团队试图通过强调他过去对以色列的支持来控制损失。</description><pubDate>Fri, 13 Oct 2023 22:50:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/trump-says-he-stands-with-netanyahu-after-a-barrage-of-gop-criticism-for-saying-he-let-us-down/articleshow/104410799.cms</guid></item><item><title>中东和西方数万人集会支持以色列和巴勒斯坦人</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/tens-of-thousands-rally-in-middle-east-west-to-support-israel-palestinians/articleshow/104409236.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104409236.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;中东、亚洲、欧洲和美国各地都爆发了支持巴勒斯坦人和反对以色列对加沙加强打击的抗议活动。各国犹太社区也举行集会声援以色列。西方国家政府对以色列表示支持，但以色列的反应引发了阿拉伯和穆斯林国家的愤怒。</description><pubDate>Fri, 13 Oct 2023 22:00:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/tens-of-thousands-rally-in-middle-east-west-to-support-israel-palestinians/articleshow/104409236.cms</guid></item><item><title>致命的拉海纳野火拨打的 911 电话显示，居民们感到恐惧和恐慌，拼命逃离</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/911-calls-from-deadly-lahaina-wildfire-show-residents-terror-and-panic-in-a-desperate-bid-to-escape/articleshow/104410938.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104410938.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;毛伊县当局公布了 8 月份毛伊岛拉海纳致命野火期间拨打 911 电话的录音。这些电话描绘了一个可怕的场景，人们拼命试图逃离地狱，司机被困在交通堵塞和火焰包围中。飓风过后的强风助长了这场野火，导致至少 98 人死亡，2000 多座建筑物被毁。</description><pubDate>Fri, 13 Oct 2023 23:28:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/911-calls-from-deadly-lahaina-wildfire-show-residents-terror-and-panic-in-a-desperate-bid-to-escape/articleshow/104410938.cms</guid></item><item><title>尽管贸易略有改善，但中国通胀数据显示经济低迷</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/business/international-business/chinas-inflation-data-show-economy-in-doldrums-despite-a-slight-improvement-in-trade/articleshow/104410889.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104410889.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;中国经济继续陷入困境，数据显示价格下跌和需求下降。 9月份消费者价格持平，批发价格下降2.5%。由于全球需求疲软，出口和进口也出现下降。国际货币基金组织下调了中国的增长预测，理由是消费者信心减弱和房地产行业危机。</description><pubDate>Fri, 13 Oct 2023 23:14:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/business/international-business/chinas-inflation-data-show-economy-in-doldrums-despite-a-slight-improvement-in-trade/articleshow/104410889.cms</guid></item><item><title>在贝鲁特，伊朗外长警告称，如果以色列继续轰炸加沙，战争可能会蔓延</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/in-beirut-irans-foreign-minister-warns-war-could-spread-if-israeli-bombardment-of-gaza-continues/articleshow/104409562.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104409562.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;伊朗外交部长侯赛因·阿米拉卜杜拉希安警告说，如果以色列不停止对加沙的袭击，暴力可能会蔓延到中东其他地区。正在该地区访问的阿米拉卜杜拉希安在与黎巴嫩官员会面时呼吁以色列停止袭击。他还会见了真主党领导人哈桑·纳斯鲁拉。</description><pubDate>Fri, 13 Oct 2023 22:12:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/in-beirut-irans-foreign-minister-warns-war-could-spread-if-israeli-bombardment-of-gaza-continues/articleshow/104409562.cms</guid></item><item><title>首架从以色列起飞的美国包机抵达雅典</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/first-us-charter-flight-out-of-israel-arrives-in-athens/articleshow/104410828.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104410828.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;在加沙冲突期间，美国国务院组织了一架包机从以色列撤离美国人。该航班降落在雅典，雅典和特拉维夫之间还计划有更多包机航班。包括联合航空、美国航空和达美航空在内的美国航空公司也增加了转机航班，以帮助美国人回国。这些航空公司暂时停止了飞往以色列的直飞航班，但立法者敦促恢复飞往特拉维夫的航班。</description><pubDate>Fri, 13 Oct 2023 22:56:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/first-us-charter-flight-out-of-israel-arrives-in-athens/articleshow/104410828.cms</guid></item></channel></rss>